  "title": "Patient Service Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assist doctor during consultations and medical procedures</li><li>Register patients and handle front counter duties</li><li>Prepare treatment rooms and medical supplies</li><li>Perform basic clinical tasks (e.g. blood pressure, temperature, height &     weight)</li><li>Handle payment, simple billing, and appointment scheduling</li><li>Maintain clinic cleanliness and adhere to infection control standards</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Passionate about working in a healthcare environment</li><li>Pleasant, patient, and service-oriented attitude</li><li>Able to work well in a team</li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><ul><li>Friendly and supportive clinic team</li><li>Training provided</li><li>Career progression opportunities within healthcare</li><li>2-3months AWS+Variable Bonus</li></ul><p>Business Edge Personnel Services Singapore </p><p>EA License No: 96C4864 </p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R26159908 (Tan Ying Ying)</p>",
